text:
Come on people, we have to wake up now. 

Righteous Judgement here: 
The lyrics are inappropriate for children. 
The short skirt, the dancing, the loaded makeup and other ways to ‘beautify’ self is also a problem. It is. 

The umbrella as she is walking into the building like she’s a queen?!

Don’t say she is a queen, because no celebrity is. 

Self praise and pride falls short under the eyes of God. Proverbs 16:18 - “Pride goes before destruction and a haughty spirit before a fall.” 

The entertainment industry screams attention, to sexualise what we ‘think’ is ‘pure’ and ‘innocent.’ 
It is far from that.

Ask yourself questions of discernment towards the wickedness this entertainment world puts in front of you.
Question = Quest I on. 
You, your life is a quest.
Quest I am on.

Barbie itself turned dark in the rise to fame, fortune and success. 

Research: ‘The Dark Truth About Barbie.’

John 8:32 -
“You shall know the truth, and the truth shall set you free.”

May The Lord Jesus Christ † be with you reader. 

God Bless you.
